name: Whisky Ginger
prepTime: 2 minutes
cookTime: 0 minutes
portions: 1

ingredients:
  - (2 oz)      Bourbon Whisky
  - (1 bottle)  Reed's Extra Ginger Ginger Beer
  - (1/4 oz)    Lime Juice
  - (1 splash)  Pomegranate Juice

steps:
  - Mix ingredients in glass with ice
  - Optionally add sliced strawberries as a garnish
